# Agent workflow — Poteto default, Ponytail fallback, QA gate

## Harness (reference library)

**Path:** `.cursor/harness/README.md`

This MDC is the **router** (classify → gate → execute). Procedures live in the harness — read the index before review, audit, debt scan, or ladder sync. Do not invent ponytail-review/audit behavior from memory.

| Task | Load |
|------|------|
| Over-engineering review (diff) | `.cursor/harness/skills/review.md` |
