## Skills scope (local only)

**Use only skills under this workspace's `.agents/skills/`.** Do not load, cite, or install from global paths (`~/.cursor/skills/`, `npx skills add -g`). Harness adapters live in `.cursor/harness/skills/`.

**Exceptions (explicit user invoke only):** `/poteto-mode` and other plugin skills the user names in the prompt — not the global Agents-tab catalog from other projects.

Install template (from repo root): `npx skills add <owner/repo@skill> -y --agent cursor`

