## Gate examples

| Prompt | Words | Complexity | Result |
|--------|------:|------------|--------|
| "fix typo line 12" | ~4 | low | Ponytail-only, no gate |
| "Add OAuth, refresh tokens, PKCE, tests, migrate users…" (+ long spec) | 250+ | high | Poteto, no gate |
| "fix auth" | ~2 | high | **Gate** — short but vague/high blast radius |
| 400-word paste + "just change the button color to blue" | long | low | **Gate** — long but simple ask |
| "refactor utils" | ~2 | mid | **Gate** — ambiguous |
